However as to what you said:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> because you have no knowledge of all of creation and how it is all going to happen</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
<br>
It doesn't matter if you personally have foreknowledge of events or not.  You are a single dominoe in the line of dominoes, not the person who tipped them and caused them to fall.<br>
<br>
If I were destined to be in a car crash tomorrow would my lack of knowledge of the coming crash cause the crash not to happen?  Of course not, that is a contradiction of predestination.<br>
